&lt;p&gt;Updating the driver version makes them go away.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is another PR that adds more tests and bumps the driver:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/647&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/647&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

